## [function __image\_button\.on\_mouse\_click__\(pos\)](#function-__image_buttonon_mouse_click__pos) {#function-__image_buttonon_mouse_click__pos}

Is called whenever the user clicks on the widget. Returns the image_id or the path to the image if no image_id has been specified.

__Arguments:__

- `pos` -- An (x, y) coordinate tuple.
	- Type: tuple

</div>

